channel.title: Random "Error connecting to server"?
channel.description: Hey guys, I was logging into my server one day to make a few changes, but it kepy saying "error connecting to server". I didn't change anything since i logged off last.. My server IP is still the same. No-ip is still working. It was working for WEEKS before this. I'm not getting any error messages or anything, it just says "error connecting to server" Keep in mind I didn't change anything since it was last working.
